# Database

- All queries in `@/lib/db/` using the Supabase **server** client
- Row Level Security enabled on all user-facing tables — users access only their own rows
- Migrations in `supabase/migrations/` run in order (001 → 002)

## Tables

- `profiles` — extends `auth.users`; auto-created on signup
- `clients` — client name, company, email, notes
- `interactions` — time spent (activity_type, duration_minutes, input_source)
- `expenses` — amount_cents linked to client (+ optional interaction)
- `deals` — revenue (pipeline | closed | lost)
- `calendar_connections` — OAuth tokens for Google/Outlook (phase 2)

## Storage

- Bucket `voice-memos` — user-scoped paths `{user_id}/{uuid}.ext`

Use typed row types from `types/database.ts`.
